# TC19: DustDetected1
# Precondition: NormalMode
# Action: detect dust
# Expected: BoostMode, CleanerDriver mode is boost.
power
start
expect power on
expect mode NormalMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode normal
expect motor moving
dust
expect power on
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
expect motorForward true
exit
